    ],
    [
      1,
      "p",
      [
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          "This is about something much bigger — it is about systemic ideological skewing of the discourse, a topic I’ve obsessed over since I wrote "
        ],
        [
          0,
          [
            18
          ],
          1,
          "my first book on the subject"
